window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>It's not easy being a rebel. So many new skills to assimilate. Never mind strategic planning, weapons expertise and the like - there's bicycle-stealing, oil-stain removal and boat steering to be mastered first. And quickly. </p> <p>It's the time of the Civil Uprisings, and two young women set out to make a difference. Their only problem? They don't know where they are. Or where they're going. Or what to do when they get there. Other than that... </p> <p>Fans of St Mary's will enjoy this glimpse into the past of some of their favourite characters. </p>"; 
